author: Business Insider
description:
Sponsored by Indeed

Indeed is redefining what it means to hire in the age of AI.

At Indeed, Chief Revenue Officer Maggie Hulce shares how AI is helping recruiters focus on streamlining the repetitive parts of hiring so they can focus on the human side - and how Indeed is making the process faster, simpler, and more human, for both job seekers and employers.

From helping candidates find opportunities that align with their goals to empowering companies to identify and grow adaptable, curious talent, AI is reshaping every stage of the hiring journey.

Watch how Indeed is using AI to unlock potential and transform the future of work. https://www.indeed.com/hire?kw=&sid=us_tmp_uc_always-on_sc_employerad_tn_brnd

author: Business Insider
description:
Sponsored by Amazon Ads

In the second episode of The Inspiration Lab, Amazon Ads Global Director of Brand Marketing, Carly Zipp, sits down with Katie Klein, Chief Investment Officer at Omnicom Media Group, to explore how advertisers can use audience-first strategies and advanced tools to turn attention into action. Katie and Carly cover everything from AI-powered solutions, to the renaissance of live programming, and the evolution of the traditional marketing funnel. 

For more, visit https://advertising.amazon.com/.
